In the strategy of the Property Department of the Riga City Council, the renovation of the VEF Palace of Culture is divided into seemingly independent sets of reconstruction works, each of which will ensure the implementation of different functions of the palace.
The first - increasing the accessibility of VEF Culture Palace and beautifying the surrounding area.
