A year later, Antonenko sang the role of Othello at London&#39;s Covent Garden Opera with great success.
Former NATO commander Breedlove&#39;s e-mail was hacked by Russian hackers.
The hackers who hacked the computers of the US Democratic National Committee (DNC) may have carried out several other cyber attacks, including the e-mail of Philip Breedlove, the former commander of NATO&#39;s European forces, and the servers of the George Soros Institute &quot;Open Society&quot;, the business news agency &quot;Bloomberg&quot; reported on Thursday. .
